                    <p>We are committed to protecting and respecting your privacy. This Privacy Statement, together with the Terms and Conditions of use of our website www.worldsbestbars.com (hereinafter referred to as the “Site”) and any other documents referred to on it, sets out the basis on which any personal data we collect from you or that you provide to us (hereinafter referred to as the “Data”) will be processed by us. Please read the following carefully to understand our treatment and use of Data.</p>

