                        <li>details of your visits to the Site (including, traffic Data, location Data, weblogs and other communication Data, whether this is required for our own billing purposes or otherwise) and the resources that you access.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <p>When you access our Site, your computer's browser provides us with information such as your IP address, browser type, access time and referring URL which is collected and used to compile statistical data on the use of our Site. This information may be used to help us to improve our Site and the services we offer.</p>

                    <div class="h2 text-transform-uppercase">3 Purposes of the processing</div>
                    <p>We use your Data that we collect, exclusively, to:</p>

