                    <p>We may also disclose your Data to those carefully selected parties so that they may contact you for the same purposes.</p>

                    <p>If you consent to that use for those purposes, please tick the relevant box situated on the forms on which we collect your Data. Further, in the event, you would have consented to that use but you finally wish to stop the use of your Data for those purposes, please contact us at any time (see Article 11 - CONTACT US below).</p>

