                    <p>All such rights shall be exercised by electronic letter, together with a copy of a piece of identity, sent to our Data Protection Compliance Officer at <a href="mailto:dataprotection@worldsbestbars.com">dataprotection@worldsbestbars.com.</a>.</p>

                    <p>We will respond to you within a reasonable period of time from your request, in compliance with applicable law.</p>

                    <p>We store your Data only for as long as necessary for the purposes of providing access to the Site and related services to you, or as permitted by applicable law.</p>

